    "description": "<u><strong>成为打牌的女巫</strong></u><br>《牌咒学院》是一款类Rogue牌组构筑游戏，你将化身女巫，修习大羊驼法术和吓人法术这些奇葩的法系。召唤怪物为你作战，搜集法咒材料施放强力法咒。一面搭配法咒打出组合法咒，一面寻找失落的灵识。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/98b0d579de4add950980f1396a924d4d.poster.avif?t=1766079654\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/98b0d579de4add950980f1396a924d4d.webm?t=1766079654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/98b0d579de4add950980f1396a924d4d.mp4?t=1766079654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>集换卡牌游戏式战斗</strong></u><br>召唤怪物保护自己，皮糙肉厚的放在前排，远程攻击的放在后排！每回合仔细管理法咒材料和精力。发动强力组合法咒，消灭各种怪物和头目！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/f44a9218b1acd855d844d396954a5cde.poster.avif?t=1766079654\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/f44a9218b1acd855d844d396954a5cde.webm?t=1766079654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/f44a9218b1acd855d844d396954a5cde.mp4?t=1766079654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>法术派系别具一格</strong></u><br>召唤强大的使魔为你效力，献祭大羊驼产生更多大羊驼，也可以转化资源召唤巨型魔像。混搭不同派系的法术，探索全新战术！魔法器具可以直接发现或者购买，能够让你的构筑更加与众不同！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/0cca702e6534ce56ee3b84c6290f9a8c.poster.avif?t=1766079654\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/0cca702e6534